Class DBQueryFactory

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--DBQueryFactory
Direct Known Subclasses:
StandardDBFactory
public abstract class DBQueryFactory
extends java.lang.Object

The DBQueryFactory is an abstract class. It contains methods to product the common queries to all the Database languages. The common queries are : - table creation - tables print - tuple insertion - tuple update - tuple find
